{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/the-other-side-hollows-komik-interaktif/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Tentukan Nasib Gadis Ini di Komik The Other Side: Hollows","content":"<p>Membaca komik biasanya jadi pengalaman yang linear. Pembaca memilih komik yang mau dibaca, membaca halaman tiap halaman, dan selesai. Pembaca disajikan cerita yang sudah ditentukan oleh <em>author-</em>nya tanpa ada campur tangan untuk mempengaruhi ceritanya sendiri.</p>\n<p>Bagaimana jika pembaca sendiri yang bisa memilih ke mana cerita akan diarahkan? Tentunya ini bukan hal yang baru, karena di masa lalu ada berbagai macam novel dan komik bergaya <strong><em>choose your own adventure.</em></strong> Perkembangan teknologi pun mengembangkan konsep ini sehingga muncul berbagai visual novel dan game konvensional dengan cerita bercabang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52828\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52828\" data-attachment-id=\"52828\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/the-other-side-hollows-komik-interaktif/attachment/01-tos-hollows/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-tos-hollows.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-tos-hollows\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-tos-hollows-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-tos-hollows.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52828\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-tos-hollows.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-tos-hollows.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/01-tos-hollows-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52828\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Buku sudah,<em> game</em> pun sudah. Gimana jadinya kalau ada komik web yang bisa dibaca di komputer dan ponsel, dan juga punya format interaktif dengan <em>ending</em> yang berbeda-beda? Mumpung Bandersnatch lagi ngetren, nggak ada salahnya buat kamu untuk mencoba komik interaktif <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/the-other-side-hollows\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Other Side: Hollows!</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/the-other-side-hollows\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Other Side: Hollows</a> adalah komik interaktif perdana dari <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CIAYO Comics</a>, di mana partisipasi kamu sebagai pembaca akan mempengaruhi <em>ending</em> dari komik ini. Komik terbaru dari seri <strong>The Other Side</strong> ini adalah buah karya tim komikus yang terdiri dari <em>editor in chief</em> Herrad, ilustrator Nyoenyo dan Aji Wzt, serta penulis Snow Rexilium, Tonny Hanggoro dan Risza Ardiansyah Perdana yang juga merangkap sebagai ilustrator.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/jangan-baca-side-curse-sendirian/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Jangan Baca The Other Side: Curse Sendirian!</a></strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52829\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52829\" data-attachment-id=\"52829\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/the-other-side-hollows-komik-interaktif/attachment/02-tos-hollows/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-tos-hollows.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-tos-hollows\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-tos-hollows-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-tos-hollows.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52829\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-tos-hollows.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-tos-hollows.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/02-tos-hollows-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52829\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Dalam komik The Other Side: Hollows, kamu harus membantu seorang gadis yang diteror makhluk halus dalam perjalanan pulangnya. Apakah ia akan berhasil? Semuanya ditentukan oleh kamu sebagai pembaca. Setiap pilihan yang kamu ambil akan mempengaruhi <em>ending</em> yang diraih. Jika salah pilih, maka <em>bad end</em> akan menanti!</p>\n<p>Lalu gimana caranya kamu menyelamatkan si gadis?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52830\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52830\" data-attachment-id=\"52830\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/the-other-side-hollows-komik-interaktif/attachment/03-tos-hollows/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-tos-hollows.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-tos-hollows\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-tos-hollows-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-tos-hollows.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52830\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-tos-hollows.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-tos-hollows.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/03-tos-hollows-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52830\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Selama membaca <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/the-other-side-hollows\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Other Side: Hollows</a>, kamu akan menemukan dua pilihan. Untuk melanjutkan cerita, kamu hanya perlu memilih salah satu dari kedua pilihan tersebut. Jika kamu membaca lewat ponsel, cukup tap satu kali pada pilihan yang kamu mau. Jika kamu membaca lewat komputer, tinggal klik satu kali saja untuk memilih.</p>\n<p>Kadang ada saatnya kamu sampai di <em>bad ending. </em>Tapi tenang saja, karena jika kamu gagal di tengah jalan, kamu bisa memilih untuk mengulang lagi dan akan dibawa kembali ke awal cerita. Kamu juga masih bisa mengulang cerita lagi setelah mendapatkan satu <em>ending</em>. Cobalah berbagai rute dan pilihan dalam<a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/the-other-side-hollows\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> The Other Side: Hollows</a> dan nikmati semua jenis <em>ending-</em>nya!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52831\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52831\" data-attachment-id=\"52831\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/the-other-side-hollows-komik-interaktif/attachment/04-tos-hollows/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-tos-hollows.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-tos-hollows\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-tos-hollows-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-tos-hollows.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52831\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-tos-hollows.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-tos-hollows.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/04-tos-hollows-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52831\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Penasaran ingin mencoba <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/the-other-side-hollows\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Other Side: Hollows</a>? Kamu bisa langsung membacanya di <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/the-other-side-hollows\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">link berikut ini</a>, hanya di<a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> CIAYO Comics</a>! Setiap pilihanmu akan menentukan nasib gadis ini, jadi memilihlah dengan bijak!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"a3242471-75e0-5b01-b8fb-363e3179d8aa"}}}